snippet.title: Five Nights at Cobson's - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
As the new night guard at the Soyjak Mental Asylum, Dr. Soyer faces the difficult task of watching over the institution's mysterious patients - and trying to make it out of his shift alive. 
Releasing May 27th, 2024.
